chore(harness): remove deprecated aura-gateway-ts sidecar

The TypeScript Express sidecar at aura-gateway-ts/ has been superseded
by aura-reasoner (Rust, direct Anthropic HTTP via reqwest) for some
time. The specs (v0.1.0 spec-02..spec-05 and v0.1.1 R17) already
marked it deprecated, no runtime path invoked it, and nothing outside
the folder itself depended on it.

- Delete aura-gateway-ts/ (Express server, package.json, lockfile, src)
- Drop TypeScript gateway entries from .gitignore
- Remove gateway sections from README.md (Optional: TypeScript Gateway,
  external deps bullet, tree entry, Gateway (optional) env table)
- Update docs/PROGRESS.md: Phase 8 marked REMOVED, Phase 16 completed,
  tree entry dropped
- Update v0.1.0 spec-01..spec-05 to remove gateway references or add
  historical notes; rewrite spec-01 section 11 around aura-reasoner
- Update v0.1.1 aura-harness-upgrade.md R17 from Recommendation to Done

Verified: cargo build --workspace and cargo test --workspace
--all-features both pass (244 unit tests, 0 failures).
